<body>
    <div id="sub-detail-header">
        <p class="sub-main-title"><span class="sub-prd-name">포테토칩 오리지널</span></p>
        <img id="sub-detail-close" class="sub-detail-close" src="img/x_icon.png">
        <hr class="sub-border-divider" />
    </div>

    <div id="sub-detail-cont">
        <div id="detail-plot-cont">
            <div id="detail-plot-area">
                <canvas id="detail-plot" class="detail-plot"></canvas>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="detail-flavor-cont">
            <div id="detail-flavor-note">
                <p class="sub-title">▷ Top 5 Flavor Note</p>
                <div id="flavor-note-group">
                    <div id="flavor-note-top">
                        <button class="btn flavor-note">Nutty</button>
                        <button class="btn flavor-note">Malty</button>
                        <button class="btn flavor-note">Sulfurous</button>
                        <button class="btn flavor-note">Savory</button>
                        <button class="btn flavor-note">Caramel</button>
                        <button class="btn flavor-note" disabled>Roasted</button>
                        <button class="btn flavor-note" disabled>Green</button>
                    </div>
                    <div id="flavor-note-bottom">
                        <button class="btn flavor-note" disabled>Fruity</button>
                        <button class="btn flavor-note" disabled>Sweet</button>
                        <button class="btn flavor-note" disabled>Meaty</button>
                        <button class="btn flavor-note" disabled>Citrus</button>
                        <!-- <button class="btn flavor-note" disabled>-</button> -->
                        <button class="btn flavor-note" disabled>-</button>
                        <button class="btn flavor-note" disabled>-</button>
                        <button class="btn flavor-note" disabled>-</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="detail-mixed-info" class="detail-mixed-info">
                <p class="sub-title">▷ 화합물 정보</p>
                <%- include('sub_table.ejs') %>
            </div>
            <div id="detail-mixed-flavor-info" class="detail-mixed-flavor-info">
                <p class="sub-title">▷ Flavor 화합물 정보</p>
                <div id="flavor-info-cont">
                    <div class="flavor-info-key">
                        <ul>
                            <li>화합물질명</li>
                            <li>Flavor Note</li>
                            <li>향 특성</li>
                            <li>향 강도</li>
                            <li>맛 특성</li>
                            <li>발견 식품</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flavor-info-value" val="sulfurous">
                        <ul>
                            <li>S-Methyl3-methylbutanethioate</li>
                            <li><span class="sub-prd-attr">Sulfurous</span></li>
                            <li>양파 또는 마늘 향과 유사한 향, 강한 유황 향</li>
                            <li>중간</li>
                            <li>-</li>
                            <li>양파, 마늘, 매운맛 계열 채소, 숙성된 치즈, 육류 가공품</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flavor-info-value" val="malty">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Butanal,2-methyl-</li>
                            <li>Nutty, Roasted, <span class="sub-prd-attr">Malty</span>, Fruity</li>
                            <li>맥아를 건조하거나 발효할 때 생성되는 독특한 향, 따뜻하고 달콤한 곡물 향</li>
                            <li>강함</li>
                            <li>달콤하고 고소한맛 (Sweet & Nutty), 약간 짭짤한맛 (Savory)</li>
                            <li>구운 음식, 견과류, 커피, 초콜릿, 발효식품</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flavor-info-value" val="roasted">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Furan,2-pentyl-</li>
                            <li><span class="sub-prd-attr">Roasted</span>, Savory, Meaty, Green, Nutty, FruityMalty, Fruity</li>
                            <li>주로 볶거나 구운과정에서 발생하는 향, 약간 탄 향이나 스모키한 느낌</li>
                            <li>강함</li>
                            <li>달콤하고 고소한맛 (Sweet & Nutty), 약간 짭짤한맛 (Savory)</li>
                            <li>견과류, 곡물, 구운 음식</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flavor-info-value" val="savory">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Furan,2-pentyl-</li>
                            <li>Roasted, <span class="sub-prd-attr">Savory</span>, Meaty, Green, Nutty, FruityMalty, Fruity</li>
                            <li>짭조름하면서도 풍미있는 향, 고기와 유사한 감칠맛 나는 향</li>
                            <li>강함</li>
                            <li>달콤하고 고소한맛 (Sweet & Nutty), 약간 짭짤한맛 (Savory)</li>
                            <li>견과류, 곡물, 구운 음식</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flavor-info-value" val="caramel">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Furan,2-ethyl-</li>
                            <li>Nutty, Roasted, <span class="sub-prd-attr">Caramel</span></li>
                            <li>설탕이 고온에서 가열될 때 생기는 달콤하고 버터같은 향</li>
                            <li>강함</li>
                            <li>달콤하고 고소한맛 (Sweet & Nutty), 약간 짭짤한맛 (Savory)</li>
                            <li>구운 음식, 음료</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flavor-info-value" val="nutty">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Butanal,3-methyl-</li>
                            <li><span class="sub-prd-attr">Nutty</span>, Roasted, Malty, Fruity</li>
                            <li>견과류 특유의 고소하고 약간 기름진 향, 바삭하면서도 고소한 향</li>
                            <li>강함</li>
                            <li>달콤하고 고소한맛 (Sweet & Nutty), 약간 짭짤한맛 (Savory)</li>
                            <li>구운 음식, 견과류, 커피, 초콜릿, 발효식품</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flavor-info-key">
                        <ul>
                            <li>화학식</li>
                            <li>분류</li>
                            <li>CAS 번호</li>
                            <li>분자량(g/mol)</li>
                            <li>용해도(물/기름)</li>
                            <li>화학반응</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flavor-info-value" val="sulfurous">
                        <ul>
                            <li>C6H12OS</li>
                            <li>Thiol</li>
                            <li>23747-45-7</li>
                            <li>132.22</li>
                            <li>잘 녹지 않음 / 잘 녹음</li>
                            <li>메티오닌 열분해 반응</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flavor-info-value" val="malty">
                        <ul>
                            <li>C5H10O</li>
                            <li>Aldehyde</li>
                            <li>96-17-3</li>
                            <li>86.13</li>
                            <li>약간 녹음 / 잘 녹음</li>
                            <li>Maillard 반응</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flavor-info-value" val="roasted">
                        <ul>
                            <li>C9H14O</li>
                            <li>Furan</li>
                            <li>3777-69-3</li>
                            <li>138.21</li>
                            <li>약간 녹음 / 잘 녹음</li>
                            <li>Maillard 반응</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flavor-info-value" val="savory">
                        <ul>
                            <li>C9H14O</li>
                            <li>Furan</li>
                            <li>3777-69-3</li>
                            <li>138.21</li>
                            <li>약간 녹음 / 잘 녹음</li>
                            <li>Maillard 반응</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flavor-info-value" val="caramel">
                        <ul>
                            <li>C6H8O</li>
                            <li>Furan</li>
                            <li>3208-16-0</li>
                            <li>96.1271</li>
                            <li>약간 녹음 / 잘 녹음</li>
                            <li>캐러멜화 반응</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flavor-info-value" val="nutty">
                        <ul>
                            <li>C5H10O</li>
                            <li>Aldehyde</li>
                            <li>590-86-3</li>
                            <li>86.1323</li>
                            <li>약간 녹음 / 잘 녹음</li>
                            <li>캐러멜화 반응</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="sub-detail-footer"></div>
</body>


<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
<script src="js/sub_detail_polar_chart.js"></script>